data.description: Introducing 200 Madison Avenue, Acworth, GA, nestled in the desirable Centennial Lakes neighborhood. This immaculate townhome offers the ideal blend of comfort and community living. This rare end unit provides added privacy, lots of natural light, and a two car garage. Situated next to guest parking, this unit is perfect for those who like to entertain. Wood floors welcome you as you enter the main level foyer. The open concept layout fosters a sense of togetherness, where the living room, kitchen, and dining room flow effortlessly, making it ideal for both daily living and entertaining. Despite its townhouse designation, the high ceilings and thoughtful design provide an open and spacious ambiance that's far from the usual townhouse experience. The three bedrooms are exceptionally large, ensuring that you have the room to create your own oasis. Whether you need space for a king-sized bed or a cozy reading nook, these bedrooms are versatile and accommodating. Added loft space can be used as an office, additional seating area, or playroom. This property is meticulously maintained, ensuring a move-in ready experience with no need for renovations. Outside, the buyer has the option to add a fence to further privatize their space. HOA covers all exterior materials, including roof, siding, and painting as well as landscaping and outside pest control. Property was newly painted, HVAc serviced in June. Community offers endless amenities including parks, playgrounds, walking paths, poo, tennis courts and more. This townhome is a canvas waiting for your personal touch. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make it your own and create a lasting legacy. Act fast because homes like these are rare finds in this desirable community!
